datavisualizer.views

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • datavisualizer.views.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
    The model unites all parts of the application. It manages xml and binary parsing as well as the info required to plot the traces in the nebula xyGraph.
    Author:
    Samy Dafir, Sophie Reischl, Dominik Baumgartner
